{"tid":2313161,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[Mac] tb3 docking 集中討論","createTime":"2020-12-05T14:23:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-07T14:09:20.000Z","uid":103759,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d625b7b7895cc0371f5bfd98dc711e8d69787608","tid":2313161,"uid":103759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T14:23:21.000Z","msg":"見Mac post 多咗人問用咩docking 好 所以諗住開個post 來討論下 <br />\ntb3 docking 同type C docking 雖然個插頭樣係一樣 但兩隻docking 支援嘅嘢可以差好遠<br />\n最明顯 type C docking 駁芒最多得4k@30Hz 而tb3 docking可以出到雙 4k@60Hz 或者單個5k@60Hz 亦都可駁到eGPU<br />\n<br />\n常見多人用嘅tb3 有 <br />\nCalDigit TS3 Plus<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n- 支援87W output <br />\n- 大量usb A/C 頭<br />\n- 有光纖audio <br />\n<br />\nOWC Thunderbolt 3 Pro Dock<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n- 有10G lan / eSATA / CF card reader <br />\n- 偏專業向 <br />\n<br />\n仲有elgato / Belkin  但佢哋嘅port 數真係太少 所以都唔推薦"},{"pid":"f1a12f47f5804fcb61c84b0f08753739d7af07a8","tid":2313161,"uid":21483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T14:27:11.000Z","msg":"見無人回，幫你推一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71b1ffbcb6ca68848a0ecc833ee3fd64075fcb18","tid":2313161,"uid":103759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f1a12f47f5804fcb61c84b0f08753739d7af07a8","tid":2313161,"uid":21483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T14:27:11.000Z","msg":"見無人回，幫你推一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T14:32:43.000Z","msg":"新開 冇乜所謂嘅 <br />\n呢個post 應該長期沉底 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為係講緊 首先要買macbook 之後仲要買tb3 docking 超低機率<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c33a2a9278f4b7a3392e522815e5450dcae4d01","tid":2313161,"uid":45830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T16:41:56.000Z